data.description: Discover your dream home with this exceptional opportunity! Nestled just minutes away from convenient amenities like Walmart and Dairy Queen, this captivating residence offers both comfort and accessibility. Embrace the tranquility of a greenbelt setting, providing a serene backdrop for your new chapter. The house is sold 'as is,' presenting a canvas for your personal touch. Step inside and experience the light and airy 2 story with brand new carpeting underfoot, adding a touch of warmth and comfort. Priced to sell, this home invites you to envision a life of convenience, comfort, and style. Don't miss the chance to make this gem your own – schedule a viewing today
